( Carnage: Thank you for the currection. I had not recieved the post 
relaying he had transformed until after I had posted Dinobots' attack.
And I shall post in small posts, to keep up with the action.)


** Dinobot growled and stood his ground as he watched Sixshot turn and aim 
towards him, then narroewd his optics as he saw the Alliance bot get hit and 
another one of his modes scrapped.
However, where was the battle if there was no challenge in it?
Dinobot moved towards Sixshot a bit, but stopping a fare distance away from 
the deadly looking tank/bot. His tail swinging behind him as he watched 
carefully.
However, he wasn't about to let the bot go with something as simply as 
before. He was going to go into stasis lock before he left him alone!
Dinobot growled and aimed his optic laser towards the center of Sixshots' 
structure, sighted and fired two quick rounds of four deadly charges.**
